This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with generating image descriptions. It could also belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it involves generating natural language descriptions. The use of LSTM and neural networks suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the use of phrases and words in the proposed model suggests that it could also belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
